---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | APIRank"
  description="APIRank privacy policy: what data we collect, what we don't collect, your GDPR/CCPA rights, and how to contact us about privacy concerns."
  canonicalUrl="https://apirank.vip/privacy/"
>
  <div class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600">Home</a>
        <span>›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Privacy</span>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 8, 2026</p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>APIRank</strong> ("we," "us," or "our") collects,
        uses, and shares information when you visit <strong>apirank.vip</strong> (the "Site").
        By using the Site, you agree to the practices described here.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">1.1 Information you provide directly</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We do not require account registration to use APIRank. If you contact us via email
        (contact@apirank.vip), we will receive whatever information you include in your message.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">1.2 Information collected automatically</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">When you visit APIRank, we and our third-party services may automatically collect:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li><strong>IP address</strong> — used for geo-targeting (e.g., to detect China for accessibility info) and abuse prevention</li>
        <li><strong>Browser type and version</strong> — used to ensure compatibility</li>
        <li><strong>Referring URL</strong> — used to understand traffic sources</li>
        <li><strong>Pages visited and time spent</strong> — used to improve content</li>
        <li><strong>Device type</strong> (mobile/tablet/desktop) — used for responsive design</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Do NOT Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We do not collect:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li>API keys, tokens, or authentication credentials (we don't have a backend service for you to log into)</li>
        <li>Payment information (all purchases happen on third-party provider sites)</li>
        <li>Personal identification beyond what is needed for site operation</li>
        <li>Cross-site tracking data (we do not sell or share user data with data brokers)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        APIRank uses minimal cookies and local storage:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Essential cookies</strong> — for site functionality (e.g., language preference)</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — via Google Analytics 4 (see Section 4)</li>
        <li><strong>Advertising cookies</strong> — via Google AdSense (see Section 5)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Disabling essential cookies may affect site functionality.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Analytics (Google Analytics 4)</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use APIRank. GA4 collects
        anonymized usage data. You can opt out by installing the
        <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-blue-600 underline">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Advertising (Google AdSense)</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        APIRank displays ads served by Google AdSense. AdSense uses cookies to serve ads based
        on your prior visits to our site and other sites on the internet. You can opt out of
        personalized advertising by visiting
        <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-blue-600 underline">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Some links on APIRank are affiliate links. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase,
        we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. Affiliate relationships do not influence
        our review rankings or recommendations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA / PIPEDA)</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Depending on your jurisdiction, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — request correction of inaccurate personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — request deletion of your personal data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
        <li><strong>Restriction</strong> — request that we limit processing of your personal data</li>
        <li><strong>Portability</strong> — request transfer of your data in a machine-readable format</li>
        <li><strong>Object</strong> — object to processing based on legitimate interest</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <strong>contact@apirank.vip</strong>. We respond within 30 days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Data Retention</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We retain analytics data for 26 months (Google Analytics default). Email inquiries are
        retained for as long as needed to address your question, then deleted. We do not retain
        user account data (we don't have user accounts).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        APIRank is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
        information from children. If you believe a child has provided us personal information,
        please contact us at contact@apirank.vip and we will delete it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. International Data Transfers</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        APIRank is hosted on Cloudflare's global CDN. By using the Site, you acknowledge that
        your information may be transferred to and processed in the United States and other
        countries where our service providers operate.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the
        top reflects the most recent change. Material changes will be announced on the homepage.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">12. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">For privacy-related questions or to exercise your rights:</p>
      <ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-gray-700">
        <li>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:contact@apirank.vip" class="text-blue-600 underline">contact@apirank.vip</a></li>
        <li>💬 Author profile: <a href="https://about.me/jasonxmai" rel="me noopener" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline">about.me/jasonxmai</a></li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
